                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-222" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.55em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.551em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.1875</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-225" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-226" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-227" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>σ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>σ</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.25</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.15</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1875</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-15">\rm \sigma=\frac{L\Delta\ d}{d\Delta\ l}\Rightarrow\Delta d=\frac{\sigma\times d\Delta\ l}{L}=\ \frac{0.25\times5\times0.15L}{L}=0.1875\ mm</script></span></p>
</span>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 3 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-228" style="width: 1.678em; top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-233"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-234" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-235" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-236" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-237" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-18-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-238" style="width: 2.498em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.051em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.01em, 2.349em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-239"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-240" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-241" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-242" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-243" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কৃতকাজ,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-277" style="width: 12.584em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.289em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1010.29em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-278"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-279" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-280" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-281" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-282" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-283" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-284" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-285" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-286" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-287" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">l</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-288" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-289" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-290" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-291" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-292" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-294" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-295" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-296" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">l</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-22">\rm W=\frac{1}{2}\times F\times l=\frac{1}{2}\times mg\times l</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.02</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.098</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-297" style="width: 11.682em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.551em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1009.51em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-298"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-299" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-300" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-301" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-302" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-303" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-304" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">9.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-305" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-306" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">0.02</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-307" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-308" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.098</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-309" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-310" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 4 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>পীড়নের মাত্রা কোনটি?</p>

                                        </div>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-38-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>50</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-544" style="width: 3.653em; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-551" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.139em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>50</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-38">\rm  50\ cm^2</script></span>&nbsp;প্রস্থচ্ছেদের ক্ষেত্রফল বিশিষ্ট তারের উপাদানের ইয়ং এর গুণাঙ্ক&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-39-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>12</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-552" style="width: 9.875em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.087em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1008.09em, 2.61em, -999.998em);                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>12</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>14</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-617" style="width: 20.904em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.133em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.822em, 1017.09em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-618"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-619" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-620" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-621" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.23em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.613em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-622"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-623" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">Y</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-624" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">A</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-625" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">l</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-626" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.39em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-627" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-628" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-722" style="width: 1.551em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.277em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1001.23em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-723"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-724" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0.4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-50">0.4 </script></span></p>
</label>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2.178</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>12</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-749" style="width: 11.6em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-53-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-773" style="width: 13.977em; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-790" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-791" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">σ<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-792" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-793" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-794" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">Y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-54-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.35</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-798" style="width: 11.969em; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-806" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-807" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.35</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বস্তুর আয়তন গুণাঙ্ক&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-55-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>7.</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-815" style="width: 9.614em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.863em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1007.86em, 2.386em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.225em;">×</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-821" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-822" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-823"><span style="display: inline-block;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-60-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mfrac></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>7.2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.15</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1.08</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-892" style="width: 28.363em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 23.24em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1023.24em, 2.994em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-893"><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-894" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-895" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">B</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-896" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-897" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-898" style="font-size: 70.7%; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>12</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>×</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>21.3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-68">\rm W=\frac{YAl^2}{2L}=\frac{2\times{10}^{12}\times0.1\times10\times{10}^{-6}\times\left(8\times{10}^{-3}\right)^2}{2\ \times\ \ 3}=21.3J</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1092" style="width: 7.912em; position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1232"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1233"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1234" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1235"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1236"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1237" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1238" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1239" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3.15</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1240" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1241" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1242"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1243"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1244" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1245"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1246"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1247" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">11</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1248" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1249"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1250"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1251" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">/</span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1252"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1253" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1254" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>3.15</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-80">\rm =\frac{1}{2}\times\left(3\right)^2\times7\times{10}^{10}=3.15\times{10}^{11}J/m^3</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-85-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>17.27</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1299" style="width: 17.133em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.018em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1014.02em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1300"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1301"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.887em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1444" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.452em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mo>∝</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-88">\rm E=\frac{1}{2}kA^2\Rightarrow E\propto A^2\Rightarrow\frac{E_2}{E_1}=\frac{A_2^2}{A_1^2}=\frac{\left(2A_1\right)^2}{A_1^2}=4</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-93-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><msqrt><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1487" style="width: 10.248em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                            <span>Question 20 </span>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1548" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">D</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.99em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1549" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1550" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1551" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.994</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.56em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1552" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.991</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.72em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1553" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1554" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.003</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1555" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1556" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">100.3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1557" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>∝</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.994</mn><mn>0.991</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1.003</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>100.3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-98">\rm \Rightarrow g\propto L\Rightarrow\ \frac{g_L}{g_D}=\frac{L_L}{L_D}=\frac{0.994}{0.991}=1.003=100.3\%</script></span>&nbsp;অর্থাৎ 0.3% বেশি।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1614" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1615" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1.25</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2.5</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo>;</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msqrt><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2.5</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3.14</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1.55</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-100">\rm =2\times1.25=2.5s ; T=2\pi\sqrt{\frac{L}{g}}\Rightarrow L=\frac{T^2g}{4\pi^2}=\frac{{2.5}^2\times9.8}{4\ \times{3.14}^2}=1.55m</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

                                        <div class="serial">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 23 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 100px; height: 101px;"></p>

<p>লেখচিত্রে একটি স্প্রিং&nbsp;এ প্রযুক্ত বলের সাথে দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি দেখানো হয়েছে। স্প্রিংটিকে 5cm প্রসারিত করা হলে, সঞ্চিত বিভবশক্তি হবে-</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>

overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>0.1</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>60</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>0.05</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0.075</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-111">\rm k=\frac{F}{x}=\frac{6}{0.1}=60Nm^{-1}\ ;\ \ E_p=\frac{1}{2}kx^2=\frac{1}{2}\ 60\times{0.05}^2=0.075J</script></span></p>

<p>বিকল্প:&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-112-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.05</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.075</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1853" style="width: 15.699em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.871em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1012.83em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1854"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1855"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.232em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1856" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1857" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 24 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

<p>স্প্রিংটিকে টেনে ছেড়ে দিলে এটি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-113-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1876" style="width: 1.12em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.896em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1000.86em, 2.349em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1877"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1878" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1879" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.043em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-113">\rm 2s</script></span>&nbsp;এ 5&nbsp;টি দোলন দেয়। স্প্রিংটির স্প্রিং ধ্রুবক কত?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>Reduced mass,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-117-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03BC;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.4</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>0.5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0.4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.22</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1913" style="width: 11.846em; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.648em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msqrt><mfrac><mi>μ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msqrt><mfrac><mi>μ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>5</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>μ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.22</mn><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>5</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>54.23</mn><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-118">\rm T=2\pi\ \sqrt{\frac{\mu}{k}}\Rightarrow\frac{2}{5}=2\pi\sqrt{\frac{\mu}{k}}\Rightarrow\left(\frac{1}{5\pi}\right)^2=\frac{\mu}{k}\Rightarrow k=\frac{0.22}{\left(\frac{1}{5\pi}\right)^2}=54.23{\rm Nm}^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>অসহ ভার&nbsp;=&nbsp;&nbsp;(অসহ পীড়ন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-41" style="width: 0.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.355em, 1000.49em, 2.092em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-42"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-43" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.703em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>×</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-6">\times </script></span>&nbsp;প্রস্থচ্ছেদের ক্ষেত্রফল)&nbsp;/g&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4.29</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mn>9.8</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2248;</mo><mn>875</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-44" style="width: 11.355em;                                         <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>2.03</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3600</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi></mrow><mn>3600</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>3600</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3600</mn></mrow><mn>2.03</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>53.2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-76" style="width: 20.945em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.174em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1017.13em, 2.461em, -999.998em); height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.39em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-81" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-96" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-97" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-98" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3600</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.23em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.613em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-99" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2.03</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.625em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-100" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-101" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-102" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-103" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">53.2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-104" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>2.03</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3600</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi></mrow><mn>3600</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>3600</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>×</mo><mn>3600</mn></mrow><mn>2.03</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>53.2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-9">\rm \frac{2}{2.03}=\frac{3600-n}{3600}\Rightarrow3600-n=\frac{2\ \times3600}{2.03}\Rightarrow n=53.2s </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সংনম্যতা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-131" style="width: 5.617em; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.26em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.264em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>7.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-235" style="width: 10.521em; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-320" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-321" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; </span>
                                    </div>

                                            <span>Question 6 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: green">Correct</span>

                                            <p>একটি ত্রুটিপূর্ণ সেকেন্ড দোলক দিনে 10 মিনিট ফাস্ট চলে। দোলকটির দোলনকাল-</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-27-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>86400</mn><mrow><mn>86400</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>600</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>86400</mn><mn>87000</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.986</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-338" style="width: 18.281em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-339"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-340"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.617em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-341" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-342" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.617em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-343" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-344" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.486em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.72em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.9em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-345" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">86400</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1003.36em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.678em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-346"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-347" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">86400</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-348" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-349" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">600</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1003.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 3.486em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.617em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-352" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.617em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-354" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-355" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.887em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.72em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.9em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-356" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">86400</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.72em, 4.141em, -999.998em); height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.89em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.887em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-358" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-359" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-360" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-361" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.986</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-362" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>86400</mn><mrow><mn>86400</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>600</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>86400</mn><mn>87000</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.986</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-27">\rm \frac{T}{2}=\frac{86400}{86400+600}\Rightarrow\frac{T}{2}=\frac{86400}{87000}\Rightarrow T=1.986s </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-33-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-418" style="width: 14.674em; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-422"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-423"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-424" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-439" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-440" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>

0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-641"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-642"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-643" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-644" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">w</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">w</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>978</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>12</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1000</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow
