class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-46">\rm w=\frac{1}{2}\frac{kv^2}{V}\Rightarrow\frac{1}{k}=\frac{v^2}{2V\times w}=\frac{\left(1000-978\right)^2\times{10}^{-12}}{2\times1000\times{10}^{-6}\times6.05\times{10}^3}=4\times{10}^{-11}Pa^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এখানে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-666" style="width: 11.314em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.15</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-686" style="width: 9.797em; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.71em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.707em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-710" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-711" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>σ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>∆</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mo>∆</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.15</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-52">\rm \sigma=\frac{L∆r}{r∆l}=\frac{L\times3}{5\times0.15L}=4</script></span></p>

<p>কিন্তু&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-53-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;lt;</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>&amp;lt;</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-712" style="width: 10.248em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.404em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.355em, 1008.36em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-713"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-714" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-715" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-716" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&lt;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-717" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">σ<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-718" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&lt;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-719" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.5</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-720" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-721" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-722" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-723" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-724" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">σ<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-725" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-726" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>σ</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>σ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-53">\rm -1<\sigma<0.5\ \ \therefore\ \sigma=4 </script></span>&nbsp;সম্ভব নয়&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 11 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: #8d8d8d">Skipped</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সমান দৈর্ঘ্যের ও সমান প্রস্থচ্ছেদের ক্ষেত্রফলবিশিষ্ট দুইটি তারে যথাক্রমে F এবং 2F&nbsp;বল প্রয়োগ করায় এদের দৈর্ঘ্য যথাক্রমে 1mm&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;4mm প্রসারিত হয়। তার দুটির ইয়ং এর গুণাঙ্কের অনুপাত––</p>

position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-785" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-786" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-787" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, serif; font-size: 82%; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">∶</span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-788" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-789" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-790" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-791" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-792" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-793" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, serif; font-size: 82%; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">∶</span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-794" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>.</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>4</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>.</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>∶</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>∶</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-54">\rm Y=\frac{FL}{Al}\Rightarrow\frac{Y_1}{Y_2}=\frac{F_1\ l_2}{F_2\ l_1}=\frac{F\ .\ \ 4}{2F\ .\ \ 1}=2\Rightarrow Y_1∶Y_2 =2∶1 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-60-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mfrac><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-820" style="width: 7.748em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-827"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.846em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em;                                             <p>0.12m বিস্তার এবং 3Hz কম্পাঙ্কসহ একটি বস্তু সরল ছন্দিত স্পন্দনে স্পন্দিত হয়। বস্তুটির সরণের রাশি হবে-</p>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 18 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: green">Correct</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>ভূ-পৃষ্ঠে ঠিক সময় দেয় এমন সেকেন্ড দোলক পাহাড়ের চূড়ায় নিলে দোলনকাল 2.06 s হয়। পাহাড়ের উচ্চতা কত?&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-86-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6400</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1187" style="width: 7.565em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.187em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1006.08em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1188"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1189"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1190" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1191"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1192" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1193" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-87-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>192</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1198" style="width: 12.625em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.33em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.518em, 1010.33em, 3.568em, -999.998em); top: -2.785em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1199"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1200" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1201" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1202" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1203" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">(</span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1204"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1205"><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1206"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.82em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1209"><span style="display: inline-block; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1211" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.95em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 19 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: green">Correct</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 110px; height: 109px;"></p>

<p>লেখচিত্রে একটি স্প্রিং&nbsp;এ প্রযুক্ত বলের সাথে দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি দেখানো হয়েছে।&nbsp; স্প্রিংটিকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-88-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>10</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1222" style="width: 2.833em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.312em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.27em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1223"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1224" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1225" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1226" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>10</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-88">10cm</script></span> প্রসারিত করা হলে, সঞ্চিত বিভবশক্তি হবে-</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>0.1</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>60</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>0.1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0.3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-93">\rm k=\frac{F}{x}=\frac{6}{0.1}=60Nm^{-1}\ ;\ \ E_p=\frac{1}{2}kx^2=\frac{1}{2}\ 60\times{0.1}^2=0.3J</script></span></p>

<p>বিকল্প:&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-94-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1293" style="width: 13.977em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>দোলনকাল একই থাকে বলে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-97-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1323" style="width: 1.928em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.559em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1001.52em, 2.584em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1324"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1325"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.576em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1326" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.33em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1327" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.58em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.576em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1328" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                                             <span>Question 22 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>দৈর্ঘ্য বরাবর সমান বল প্রয়োগ করায় একই পদার্থের নিম্নোক্ত 4 টি তারের মধ্যে কোনটির দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি সবচেয়ে বেশি হয়?</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-108-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1413" style="width: 7.666em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.273em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1006.27em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1414"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1415" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1416" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1417" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.027em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1418"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1419" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1420" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.605em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1421"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1422" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">A</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1423" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">ℓ</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.03em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.027em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1424" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1425" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">ℓ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1426" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1427" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1428" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.605em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1429" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">A</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.66em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.658em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi>ℓ</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>ℓ</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-108">\rm Y=\frac{FL}{A\ell}\Rightarrow\ell\propto\frac{L}{A}</script></span>&nbsp;[F,Y ধ্রুবক]</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-109-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1430" style="width: 6.314em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.363em, 1000.58em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.605em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.285em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1436"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.576em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>ℓ</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-109">\rm \ell\propto\frac{L}{r^2}\ L=1m </script></span>&nbsp;ও&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-110-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1444" style="width: 9.756em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1655" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1656" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1657" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1658" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>∆</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>×</mo><mo>∆</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>4.053</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>50</mn></mrow></mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>14803.8</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>≈</mo><mn>1.5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-120">\rm B=\frac{PV}{∆V}\Rightarrow V=\frac{B\times∆V}{P}=\frac{3\times{10}^{-6}}{4.053\times{10}^{-6}\times50}m^3=14803.8\ cc\approx1.5\times{10}^4\ cc</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-128-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></msqrt></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1783" style="width: 3.404em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.789em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1002.79em, 2.707em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1784"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1785" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1786" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1787" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1788" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.95em, 4.387em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-1789"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.33em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1790"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1791" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1000.37em, 1.232em, -999.998em); top: -1.555em; left: 0.576em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.039em; border-top: 1.3px solid; width: 0.371em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.322em, 1000.62em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.891em; left: 0em;"><span><span style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.07em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></msqrt></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-128">\rm T\propto\frac{1}{\sqrt g}</script></span>;&nbsp;পাহাড়ের উপর g কমবে, তাই T বাড়বে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 19 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>দুটি সমান দৈর্ঘ্যের&nbsp;&nbsp;তারের ব্যাস যথাক্রমে&nbsp;2mm&nbsp;ও&nbsp;5mm.&nbsp;এদের সমান বলে টানা হলে প্রথম তারটির দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি দ্বিতীয়টির 4&nbsp;গুণ হয়। কোন তারটি অধিক স্থিতিস্থাপক?</p>

<div class="row questionBlock">

    <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 20 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 180px; height: 86px;"></p>

<p>চিত্রের মতো করে 2m দীর্ঘ AB তারের মধ্যবিন্দুতে 5 kg ভরের বস্তু ঝুলালে তারটি আনুভূমিকের সাথে 10° করে নিচে নেমে যায়। এক্ষেত্রে তারের ইয়ং এর গুণাঙ্ক&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-127-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi>N</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2431" style="width: 7.64em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.261em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1006.26em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2432"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2433" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2434" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2435" style="padding-left: 0.225em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.79em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.97em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2436"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2437"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2438" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1.015</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1.015</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2.031</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mo>∆</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.031</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>;</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1.58</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></msup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi>π</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7.09</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.07</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-132">\rm F=5\times9.8=49\ N \\ L=2l=2m\ ;l=1m\ \ \therefore l^\prime=\frac{1}{cos⁡(10°)}=1.015m \\ \therefore L^\prime=2l^\prime=2\times1.015=2.031\ m \\ \therefore ∆l=L'-L=0.031 m ; Y=2×10^{11}Nm^{-2} \\ \therefore Y=\frac{FL}{A\Delta l}\Rightarrow A=\frac{FL}{Y\Delta l}=1.58\times{10}^{-8}\\ \Rightarrow r=\sqrt{\frac{A}{\pi}} \therefore r=7.09\times{10}^{-5}m=0.07\ mm \rm </script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-137-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>U</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Y</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2667" style="width: 19.182em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.699em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.822em, 1015.7em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2668"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2669"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2670"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2671" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">U</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2672" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2673" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2674" style="font-size: 70.7%; </span>
            </div>
    </div>

            </div>

overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.097em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>σ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mi>D</mi></mfrac><mfrac><mi>l</mi><mi>L</mi></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.01</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-151">\Rightarrow \sigma =\frac{\frac{d}{D}}{\frac{l}{L}}=\frac{dL}{Dl}=\frac{0.01\times{10}^{-3}\times1}{5\ \times{10}^{-3}\times2\times{10}^{-2}}=0.1</script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row questionBlock">

    <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 26 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>কোনো বস্তুর উপর প্রযুক্ত আয়তন পীড়ন&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-152-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>3.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3004" style="width: 8.906em; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.395em; left: 1.008em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3012"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3013"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3014" style="font-size: 70.7%; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-164-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3198" style="width: 0.658em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-165-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>3.267</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.003</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3201" style="width: 19.715em;     <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 29 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>একটি ফাঁপা গোলককে পানি দিয়ে পূর্ণ করে একটি সুতার সাহায্যে ঝুলিয়ে সরল দোলক তৈরি করা হল। এখন, গোলকের তলায় ছিদ্র করে দিলে যদি পানি পড়তে থাকে তাহলে প্রাথমিকভাবে দোলনকালের কী পরিবর্তন হবে?</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row questionOptions">
            <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                        <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                        <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>একই থাকবে</p>
</label>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                        <span class="input-group-text">B</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                        <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>বাড়বে</p>
</label>
                        <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                        <span class="input-group-text">C</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                        <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>কমবে</p>
</label>
                        
                    </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">

            <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বাড়বে; কারণ, পানি পড়তে থাকলে গোলকের ভরকেন্দ্র নিচে নামতে থাকবে, ফলে কার্যকরী দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি পাবে।</p>
</span>

                    <span>Question 30 </span>

                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>আয়তন গুণাঙ্ক এবং কাঠিন্যের গুণাঙ্ক যথাক্রমে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-171-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>18</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3282" style="width: 8.571em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3489" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3490" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3491"><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.42em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; \Rightarrow n=235.514\ s 
</script></span></p>

                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 33 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>স্থির লিফটে কোনো সরল দোলকের দোলনকাল T ।&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-182-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi>g</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3528" style="width: 0.859em; </span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

\Rightarrow\ T_2=\sqrt2\times T_1=\sqrt2 \times 1.2=1.7s </script></span></p>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 1 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-1-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1" style="width: 6.112em;                                 <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-41" style="width: 7.01em; </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-58" style="width: 14.756em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-80" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-81" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>π</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>π</mi><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-7">\rm \omega=6\pi\Rightarrow A\omega=6\pi\therefore A=\frac{6\pi}{6\pi}=1</script></span></p>

<p>বিস্তার&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-8-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-82" style="width: 5.125em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.182em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1004.1em, 2.461em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-86" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-89" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><msqrt><msup><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-95" style="width: 8.404em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>স্প্রিংদ্বয় সমান্তরাল সংযোগে রয়েছে।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>40</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>80</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>120</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-157" style="width: 12.379em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-19-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mfrac><mn>36</mn><mn>18</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-223" style="width: 7.625em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.232em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1006.23em, 2.953em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-224"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-225" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-226" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-227" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-228"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-229" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-230" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-231" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-232" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-233" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-234"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-235" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-236" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.86em, 4.428em, -999.998em); top: -3.482em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-237"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; font-family: MathJax_Main;">36</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.227em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.617em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.99em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-240" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-241" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.097em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mfrac><mn>36</mn><mn>18</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-19">\rm \omega=\frac{2\pi}{T}=\frac{2\pi}{\frac{36}{18}}=\pi </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 6 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি m&nbsp;ভরের বস্তু ঘর্ষণবিহীন একটি তলে v&nbsp;বেগে চলার সময় একটি k-বল ধ্রুবক বিশিষ্ট স্প্রিংয়ের সাথে ধাক্কা লেগে স্প্রিংকে x-পরিমাণ সংকুচিত করলে k&nbsp;=?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.867em, 1001.1em, 1.186em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.05em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.392em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-23">\rm \frac{v}{mx} </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-24-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-284" style="width: 12.502em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-294" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <span>Question 8 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>1.5 m দৈর্ঘ্যের&nbsp;একটি ধাতব তারের এক প্রান্ত আটকে রেখে অপর প্রান্তে ভার ঝুলালে 2 mm দৈর্ঘ্য প্রসারণ হয়। তারের ব্যাস&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>σ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-32-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-470" style="width: 16.395em;
