                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 80px; height: 129px;"></p>

<p>যদি স্টিল ও তামার তারের ব্যাস, দৈর্ঘ্য এবং ইয়ংয়ের গুণাঙ্কের অনুপাত যথাক্রমে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-33-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>q</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-500" style="width: 3.467em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.833em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.678em, 1002.8em, 2.535em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-501"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-502" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">p</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-503" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-504" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.151em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-505" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">q<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-506" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-507" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.151em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-508" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.27em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.866em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">q</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-33">\rm p,\ q,\ r</script></span> হয় তবে স্টিল ও তামার তারের দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধির অনুপাত-</p>

xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Y</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi></msub></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-38">\rm \Delta l=\frac{FL}{AY}\Rightarrow\frac{\Delta l_s}{\Delta l_c}=\frac{L_s}{L_c}\times\frac{{A_c}^2}{{A_s}^2}\times\frac{Y_c}{Y_s}\times\frac{F_s}{F_c}</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-39-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>q</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>7</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>7</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>q</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-617" style="width: 10.822em; </span>
                                    </div>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1000.37em, 1.232em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.322em, 1000.62em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.891em; left: 0em;"><span><span style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.17em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-152" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-153" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-158" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.82em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.875em; left: 0.986em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 0.125em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.748em, 1001.03em, 4.797em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-159" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.448em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></msqrt></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></msqrt><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msqrt></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></msqrt><mo>×</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></msqrt></mrow></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-12">\rm T\propto\frac{1}{\sqrt g}\Rightarrow\frac{T_1}{T}=\frac{\sqrt g}{\sqrt{g\ +\ \frac{g}{2}}}\Rightarrow T_1=\sqrt g\times\frac{\sqrt2}{\sqrt3\ \sqrt g}T=\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}T </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: red">Incorrect</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">2m লম্বা ও 2mm ব্যাসবিশিষ্ট একটি তারের দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি 0.25&nbsp;mm হলে তারটির ব্যাসার্ধ কত হ্রাস পাবে? <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-160" style="width: 4.547em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.728em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1003.62em, 2.61em, -999.998em);                                             </div>

<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-19-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-256" style="width: 16.273em;                                             <span>Question 8 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি তার ছিঁড়ে যাওয়ার পূর্ব মুহূর্ত পর্যন্ত 40 কেজি ভার সহ্য করতে পারে। তারটিকে সমান দুই ভাগ করা হলে প্রতিটি ভাগ যে ভার সহ্য করতে পারে তার পরিমাণ–</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p style="text-align: justify;">অসহ ভার বস্তুর উপাদানের ওপর নির্ভরশীল, তাই দুটি ভাগ 40 কেজি ভারই সহ্য করবে।</p>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
সরল দোলন গতিসম্পন্ন একটি কণার সরণ, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-20-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-287" style="width: 7.528em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.149em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1006.08em, 2.498em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-288"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-289" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-290" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-291" style="padding-left: 0.263em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.343em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.45em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-292"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.579em, 1000.49em, 3.839em, -999.998em); top: -4.544em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.094em, 1000.86em, 4.287em, -999.998em); top: -4.022em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-294" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.151em;">sin</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-295"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-296" style="padding-left: 0.151em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-297"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-298" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-299" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-300" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-20">\rm x=\sqrt5\sin{2\pi t}</script></span>&nbsp;মিটার।</p>

                                </div>

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-25-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-330" style="width: 10.863em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 10 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: green">Correct</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সাম্যাবস্থান থেকে 2m দূরে কণাটির গতিশক্তি ও বিভবশক্তির অনুপাত–</p>

                                        </div>

                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.047em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-30">\rm A=\sqrt5\ ;\ \frac{E_k}{E_p}=\frac{\frac{1}{2}k\left(A^2-x^2\right)}{\frac{1}{2}kx^2}=\frac{5-4}{4}=\frac{1}{4}\ &nbsp;</script></span><br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-435" style="width: 7.379em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.355em, 1005.99em, 2.584em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-436"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-437" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-438" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-439" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-440" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-441" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-442" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-443" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-444" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">p</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-445" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-446" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-447" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-448" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.398em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-31">\rm \therefore E_k:E_p=1:4</script></span>&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 11 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: green">Correct</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি সেকেন্ড দোলকের দৈর্ঘ্য ঢাকায় 1m এবং রাজশাহীতে 0.96m। কোন বস্তুকে রাজশাহী থেকে ঢাকায় নিলে এর ওজন কতগুণ বাড়বে?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-36-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><msqrt><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>[</mo><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-469" style="width: 14.223em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.641em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1011.6em, 2.994em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-470"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-471" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-472" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-473" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-474" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-475"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.035em, 1000.82em, 4.633em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-476"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-477"><span style="display: inline-block; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.33em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-479" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.58em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.576em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.9em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.834em; left: 0.986em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 0.207em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-554" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.99em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.994em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-555" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-556" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.092em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.93em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.465em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.982em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-557"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-558" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-559" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-560" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">24</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-561" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">24</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.09em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.092em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-562" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-563" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-564" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-565" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">24</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.428em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.998em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>100</mn><mn>96</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>25</mn><mn>24</mn></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>25</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mn>24</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>24</mn></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-38">\rm \therefore\frac{W_D}{W_R}=\frac{mg_D}{mg_R}=\frac{L_D}{L_R}=\frac{100}{96}=\frac{25}{24}\\ &nbsp;
\therefore\frac{W_D-W_R}{W_R}=\frac{25-24}{24}=\frac{1}{24}&nbsp;</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 160px; height: 101px;"></p>

<p>প্রতি চারভাগের একভাগ সরণে দশা পার্থক্য হবে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-583" style="width: 2.051em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.682em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1001.52em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-584"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-585"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-586" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">(</span></span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-587"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-588"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-589" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-590" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-591" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-592" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-43">\left(\frac{2\pi}{4}\right)</script></span> or&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-593" style="width: 0.822em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 13 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: green">Correct</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">স্থির তাপমাত্রায় 25 বায়ুমণ্ডলীয় চাপ প্রয়োগে একটি বস্তুর আয়তনের পরিবর্তন 0.05% হলো। এর আয়তনের স্থিতিস্থাপক গুণাঙ্ক কত?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-49-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>25</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1.013</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><mn>0.0005</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>5.065</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mn>9</mn></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="width: 21.477em; </span>
                                    </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></msqrt></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-713" style="width: 3.895em; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-781" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -1.198em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-51">\rm \frac{T_1}{T_2}=\sqrt{\frac{g_2}{g_1}}=\sqrt{\frac{\left(R+h_1\right)^2}{\left(R+h_2\right)^2}}=\frac{R+h_1}{R+h_2}&nbsp;</script></span><br>
অর্থাৎ,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-783" style="width: 9.551em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.83em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1007.83em, 2.338em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-792" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">h</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-793" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-794" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-795" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-796" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-797" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>∝</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>∝</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-52">\rm T\propto\left(R+h\right)\Rightarrow T\propto h</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-101"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-102"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-103" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-104" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-105" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-109" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-110" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">9</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-111" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-112" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">N</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-113"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-115"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-116"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-117" style="font-size: 70.7%; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

স্থিতিস্থাপক গুণাঙ্কের মাত্রা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-164" style="width: 6.355em; top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-165"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-166" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-167" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-168" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">[</span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-169"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-170" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">M</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-171"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-173"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-174"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-175" style="font-size: 70.7%;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 4 </span>
                                        </div>

                                            <p>অসহ বল কোনটি?</p>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>বস্তুর একক ক্ষেত্রফলের উপর লম্বভাবে উদ্ভূত বল</p>
</label>

</label>

</label>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>D</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>0.005</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-247" style="width: 12.912em; <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-285" style="width: 8.977em; </span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কম্পাঙ্কের পরিবর্তন&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2.01</mn></mfrac></mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-303" style="width: 6.928em;                             <div class="row question">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
কোন সরল ছন্দিত স্পন্দনে স্পন্দিত কণার বিস্তার 3cm এবং সর্বোচ্চ বেগ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-20-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5.28</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-375" style="width: 5.181em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.249em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1004.25em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-376"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-377" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5.28</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-378" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-379" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-380"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.38em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.37em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-381" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-382"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-383"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-384" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-385" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mn>6</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-386" style="width: 0.933em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-25-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mn>176</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.0357</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-446" style="width: 11.682em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 11 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">সরল ছন্দিত স্পন্দনরত কোনো কণার গতি সরণের সর্বোচ্চ অবস্থান থেকে শুরু হলে, আদি দশা–</p>

                                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.997em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.452em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msqrt><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msqrt><mfrac><mn>0.1</mn><mn>9.8</mn></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>0.63</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-29">\rm T=2\pi\sqrt{\frac{e}{g}}=2\pi\sqrt{\frac{0.1}{9.8}}=0.63\ sec </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-32-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mn>9.8</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>51.02</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-532" style="width: 19.92em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-570" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">9.8</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.88em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mn>9.8</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>51.02</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-32">\rm P=\frac{mg}{A}\Rightarrow m=\frac{PA}{g}=\frac{5\times{10}^8\times1\times{10}^{-6}}{9.8}=51.02\ kg </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সরল ছন্দিত স্পন্দনের বৈশিষ্ট্য–<br>
(i) গতি পর্যাবৃত্ত<br>
(ii) ত্বরণ সরণের সমানুপাতিক<br>
(iii) গতি সরলরৈখিক<br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
